<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Corona Screening App</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box pb-5">
        <div class="container pt-5">
            <img src="../static/img/logo.png" alt="Corona App">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 col-8">
                    <h1>COVID-19 Screening Tool</h1>
                    <p>Use this self-assessment tool to help determine whether you need to be tested for COVID- 19.</p>
                    <p>You can complete this assessment for yourself or on behalf of someone else, if they are not able.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-4 flex-center">
                    <img src="/static/img/covid19screen.png" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <a href="fever" class="btn btn-primary">Start Screening</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid p-md-3">
        <h1 class="p-3 pb-0">More Information</h1>
        <a href="covidInfo">
            <div class="card p-3 mb-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction: row;">
                <div class="col-3 img-style">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/static/img/virus.png" alt="Card image cap">
                </div>
            
                <div class="card-body col-6">
                    <h5 class="card-title">What is COVID-19?</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Coronavirus disease (COVID-19) is an infectious disease...</p>
             
                </div> 
                <div class="col-2 arrow">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><!--! Font Awesome Free 6.4.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. --><path d="M310.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-192 192c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L242.7 256 73.4 86.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l192 192z"/></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="#">
            <div class="card p-3 mb-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction: row;">
                <div class="col-3 img-style">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/static/img/symptoms.png" alt="Card image cap">
                </div>
            
                <div class="card-body col-6">
                    <h5 class="card-title">What are its Symtomps</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">The COVID-19 virus affects different people in different ways...</p>
             
                </div> 
                <div class="col-2 arrow">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><!--! Font Awesome Free 6.4.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. --><path d="M310.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-192 192c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L242.7 256 73.4 86.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l192 192z"/></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a href="#">
            <div class="card p-3 mb-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction: row;">
                <div class="col-3 img-style">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/static/img/prevent.png" alt="Card image cap">
                </div>
            
                <div class="card-body col-6">
                    <h5 class="card-title">How can you prevent it?</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">There's currently no vaccine to prevent coronavirus disease...</p>
             
                </div> 
                <div class="col-2 arrow">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><!--! Font Awesome Free 6.4.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. --><path d="M310.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-192 192c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L242.7 256 73.4 86.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l192 192z"/></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        
    </div>
        
    


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>